        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[最近在清理我放在瀏覽器裡面的書籤，搭配最近架設的 Homelab ，以下是我的 SOP：]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>最近在清理我放在瀏覽器裡面的書籤，搭配最近架設的 Homelab ，以下是我的 SOP：</p>
<ol>
<li>它是 GitHub 專案。<!-- -->
<ol>
<li>它超過兩個月沒更新：Clone 下來丟 <a href="https://github.com/go-gitea/gitea" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Gitea</a>。</li>
<li>否則：餵給 <a href="https://tt-rss.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Tiny Tiny RSS</a> 訂閱<sup><a href="https://flyskypie.github.io/posts/2025-04-28_post#user-content-fn-github-rss-86075f" id="user-content-fnref-github-rss-86075f" data-footnote-ref="true" aria-describedby="footnote-label">1</a></sup>。</li>
</ol>
</li>
<li>它是 PDF：丟 <a href="https://github.com/Kareadita/Kavita" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Kavita</a>。</li>
<li>它是圖片：丟 <a href="https://github.com/pinry/pinry" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Pinry</a>。</li>
<li>它是 YouTube 影片：丟 <a href="https://github.com/jellyfin/jellyfin" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Jellyfin</a>。</li>
<li>它的主要價值是平台價值：暫時保留。</li>
<li>它是維基百科：暫時保留。</li>
<li>其他不宜直接備份原因：暫時保留。</li>
<li>否則：備份到 <a href="https://github.com/ArchiveBox/ArchiveBox" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">ArchiveBox</a></li>
</ol>
<section data-footnotes="true" class="footnotes"><h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_mpuI sr-only" id="footnote-label">Footnotes<a href="https://flyskypie.github.io/posts/2025-04-28_post#footnote-label" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Footnotes" title="Direct link to Footnotes">​</a></h2>
