<li><a href="https://github.com/Lissy93/dashy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://github.com/Lissy93/dashy</a>
<ul>
<li>18.1k ⭐</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><a href="https://github.com/ajnart/homarr" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://github.com/ajnart/homarr</a>
<ul>
<li>6.2k ⭐</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><a href="https://github.com/gethomepage/homepage" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://github.com/gethomepage/homepage</a>
<ul>
<li>19.8k ⭐</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><a href="https://github.com/bastienwirtz/homer" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://github.com/bastienwirtz/homer</a>
<ul>
